I think it's possible to have multiple `RecurseInfo` objects at the same location. Take the following query, for example:
```
{
    Foo {
        out_Foo_Foo @recurse(depth: 2) {
            name @output(out_name: "out_foos")
        }
        in_Foo_Foo @recurse(depth: 2) {
            name @output(out_name: "in_foos")
        }
    }
}
```

I think the `Foo___1` location is going to have both `RecurseInfo` objects associated with it. Based on that, I think the current approach is fine.

